{"word":"ἀπόδοσις","slug":"ἀπόδοσις","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀπόδοσις</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀποδίδωμι'><el>ἀποδίδωμι</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a giving back, restitution, return</i>, <el>τινος</el> of a thing, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, attic<p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>payment</i>, <el>τοῦ μισθοῦ</el> <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}